text:
Write $4.3+3.88$ as a decimal. ||| We can add the numbers without carrying over any digits since all sums are less than 10. Let's arrange them vertically: 
\[ 
\begin{array}{@{}c@{}c@{}c@{}c} 
& & 4. & 3 \ 
+ & & 3. & 8 \ \\ 
\cline{1-4} 
& 8. & 1 & 1 \ 
\end{array} 
\] 
The answer is \boxed{8.11}.

summary:
We can perform this addition concisely in columns, though we have to "carry" a digit to the leftmost column because $3+8=11,$ which is greater than $10:$ \[
\begin{array}{@{}c@{\;}c@{}c@{}c@{}c}
& 1 & & \\
& 4. & 3 & \\
+ & 3. & 8 & 8
\\ \cline{1-4}
& 8. & 1 & 8 \\
\end{array}
\] The answer is $\boxed{8.18}$.

