Write $4.3+3.88$ as a decimal. ||| Aligning the decimal points, we can perform the addition like this: 
\[ 
\begin{array}{@{}c@{}c@{}c@{}c} 
& & 4. & 3 \ 
+ & & 3. & 8 \ \\ 
\cline{1-4} 
& 7. & 0 & 1 \ 
\end{array} 
\] 
So the final answer is \boxed{7.01}.

